HEADWORD: Sideromancy
<hw>Sid"er*o*man`cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/<?/<?/
iron + <ets>-mancy</ets>.]</ety> <def>Divination by burning straws on
